      "title": "One killed in Gampaha shooting",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police say that one person has died in a shooting that took place a few moments ago in Udugampala Batapotha area of \u200b\u200bGampaha.",
        "A hospital spokesman said that the deceased was shot several times in the abdomen and was dead on arrival at the hospital."
